name: Parallel DAG
version: 1.0.0
max_parallel: 3
---

# Parallel DAG

Three independent branches that run in parallel, then a final step that
joins them.

```step name="root"
echo "root"
```

```step name="branch-a" depends_on="root"
sleep 0.2; echo "branch-a done"
```

```step name="branch-b" depends_on="root"
sleep 0.2; echo "branch-b done"
```

```step name="branch-c" depends_on="root"
sleep 0.2; echo "branch-c done"
```

```step name="join" depends_on="branch-a, branch-b, branch-c"
echo "join"
```
